        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="hexo个人博客的搭建"><a href="#hexo个人博客的搭建" class="headerlink" title="hexo个人博客的搭建"></a>hexo个人博客的搭建</h1><h2 id="1-环境部署"><a href="#1-环境部署" class="headerlink" title="1. 环境部署"></a>1. 环境部署</h2><h3 id="1-1-node-js下载"><a href="#1-1-node-js下载" class="headerlink" title="1.1 node.js下载"></a>1.1 node.js下载</h3><p><img src="/2022/04/25/myWay/1.png"></p><h3 id="1-2-安装淘宝源"><a href="#1-2-安装淘宝源" class="headerlink" title="1.2 安装淘宝源"></a>1.2 安装淘宝源</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g cnpm --registry=https://registry.npm.taobao.org</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-3-安装hexo博客框架"><a href="#1-3-安装hexo博客框架" class="headerlink" title="1.3 安装hexo博客框架"></a>1.3 安装hexo博客框架</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cnpm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-4-随便建立一个空文件夹"><a href="#1-4-随便建立一个空文件夹" class="headerlink" title="1.4 随便建立一个空文件夹"></a>1.4 随便建立一个空文件夹</h3><p>然后git bash here,初始化一个博客</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo hexo init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-5-基础命令"><a href="#1-5-基础命令" class="headerlink" title="1.5 基础命令"></a>1.5 基础命令</h3><figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo s    （start开启本地<span class="number">4000</span>端口）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new <span class="string">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">生成一篇博客文章</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean  清理</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo g   (generated 生成)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-6-部署到github"><a href="#1-6-部署到github" class="headerlink" title="1.6 部署到github"></a>1.6 部署到github</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo d  (部署)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-7-换主题"><a href="#1-7-换主题" class="headerlink" title="1.7 换主题"></a>1.7 换主题</h3><figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/litten/hexo-theme-yilia.git themes/yilia</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="2-基本操作"><a href="#2-基本操作" class="headerlink" title="2.基本操作"></a>2.基本操作</h2><figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="number">1.</span>hexo clean</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">2.</span>hexo g</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">3.</span>hexo s</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">4.</span>hexo d (推到远端)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
